title: Latest news & 'Win Wess' Toaster!'
itunes:title: Latest news & 'Win Wess' Toaster!'
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- discuss the latest NFL news including the Redskins' quarterback situation, C.J. Spiller's potential with the Saints and more. Plus, it's Wess versus our listeners in a new round of 'Win Wess' Toaster!'.
